    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior is clean and the paint retains a nice shine, you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. The interior is tidy and smoke-free, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
