    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this beauty is in such incredible shape, it still feels brand new! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm really looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example of BMW\u2019s engineering pinnacle. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features a recently overhauled VANOS system and precise valve lash adjustments, ensuring the individual throttle bodies deliver telepathic throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a refreshed subframe\u2014proactively reinforced\u2014and a limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The suspension has been subtly enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers for superior damping control without compromising the chassis' iconic balance. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays zero paint imperfections and retains its factory-spec structural integrity. A truly turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
