      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom-fresh, mint condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory paint finish, recently enhanced with a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster. There are absolutely no chips, dings, or scratches to be found on the bodywork or the pristine alloy wheels. Inside, the premium leather interior remains supple and fragrant, showing zero signs of wear, creasing, or fading; the carpets have been protected by thick floor mats since new. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealership, with all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. This is a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who demands the very best, this car represents a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in its peak form.",
